      <div class="hero-content">
        <h2>Strawberry Bars</h2>
        <p>Sweet crumbly crust with a fruity center.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="recipe-list">
    <img src="../images/strawberry-bars.jpg" alt="Strawberry Bars" style="width:100%; max-width:600px; border-radius:12px;">
    <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>1 cup butter, softened</li>
      <li>¾ cup sugar</li>
      <li>2¼ cups flour</li>
      <li>½ tsp salt</li>
      <li>1½ cups strawberry jam</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Instructions:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C). Grease a 9x13-inch pan.</li>
      <li>Cream butter and sugar. Mix in flour and salt until crumbly.</li>
      <li>Press ⅔ into pan. Spread with jam. Crumble remaining dough on top.</li>
      <li>Bake for 30–35 minutes. Cool completely before slicing.</li>
    </ol>
  </main>

